{"tid":454684,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(3部電影齊上映)想擺脫「MK活地阿倫」？ Stephy：會唔會變咗油麻地呢","createTime":"2017-11-01T11:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T16:23:23.000Z","uid":156068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ca78e74ff00ddba76e807a04d55f3ee0b47342b3","tid":454684,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T11:29:04.000Z","msg":"鄧麗欣(Stephy)噚晚到金鐘太古廣場，出席「香港亞洲電影節2017」開幕禮，Stephy有份演出嘅電影《藍天白雲》，同劉嘉玲監製與主演嘅電影《以青春的名義》為開幕電影。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講到Stephy最近先後有3部電影上映，成為影壇大紅人，佢就話其實《藍》片係張經緯導演、爾冬陛監製嘅《藍》片係3年前作品。Stephy都話好緊張，擔心香港觀眾反應，佢話:「今次好唔同，對待角色好認真，未聽到觀眾意見之前睇咗一次，唔係好專心，因為掛住睇番3年前個樣。今次會用番觀眾身份去睇。」<br />\n<br />\n佢話今日會做杜汶澤導演嘅戲《空手道》宣傳，套戲聽日上映。原本都擔心自己打自己，但希望觀眾留意到自己脫出以前嘅框框。當記者問到是否脫出「MK活地阿倫」葉念琛嘅框框時，佢講笑反問:「唔知會唔會變咗油麻地呢。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/01/192832_33fbe381c43be99ea01e47bf97050fcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F01%2F192832_33fbe381c43be99ea01e47bf97050fcd.jpg&h=22390a04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/01/192832_e6fc1bd4e03783b21a03e438d39c9dd1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F01%2F192832_e6fc1bd4e03783b21a03e438d39c9dd1.jpg&h=ef701c32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/01/192832_56ad2e119c27b4ecbc70fc116d2c2270.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F01%2F192832_56ad2e119c27b4ecbc70fc116d2c2270.jpg&h=72b2fdd2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9eff9e11b0cb5aeda3e7e65e48c5d9a9eccf7c7","tid":454684,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T12:03:50.000Z","msg":"個額<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78af4d1cf3525578fd067b3851ec52f3e5a403d0","tid":454684,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T12:06:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個額<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身都高<br />\n<br />\n有m額迹象<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31acd7df5740a8eb00f5a43fbbe4212ec3380a7d","tid":454684,"uid":61173,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:23:23.000Z","msg":"走哂樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果陣同刀甲一齊果樣仲好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}